						<td><h3>Never lose another number.</h3>
			<p>Virgin Mobile's Contact Vault makes it easy to store and  manage your contacts online. With Contact Vault, you can automatically backup  and transfer all of your contacts to a new phone without having to re-enter  them manually, one-by-one. In case your phone is lost or stolen, you can erase  the contacts from your missing phone without losing all the information stored  on our Web site. </p>
