				<li>Restore existing contacts to a new phone, quickly and       easily.</li>
				<li>Manage contacts online and transfer them to your phone,       or vice versa.</li>
				<li>Import contacts from an external address book - like       Microsoft Outlook, Yahoo!, and others.</li>
